	</div>

	<div id="t_82_9" style="position: absolute; left: 64.32%; top:30.15%;" class="c_82_1">
		&ndash;<span class="c_82_2">Charles Evans Hughes</span>
	</div>

	<div id="t_82_10" style="position: absolute; left: 67.75%; top:32.89%;" class="c_82_3">
